      public void printTree​(T root)
      Prints ascii representation of binary tree. Parameter hspace is minimum number of spaces between adjacent node labels. Parameter squareBranches, when set to true, results in branches being printed with ASCII box drawing characters.
      Parameters:
      root - The root node.
